headline: DuPont Launches Liveo™ C6-8XX Liquid Silicone Rubber Series for Healthcare Applications
summary: DuPont (NYSE:DD) today announced the launch of Liveo™ C6-8XX Liquid Silicone Rubber (LSR), a new USP Class VI (C6) series of medical-grade, two-part silicone elastomers engineered to meet the stringent requirements of medical device applications.
